<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id440285f2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s742"><num value="742">§ 742.</num><heading> Basis of transferee partner’s interest</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The basis of an interest in a partnership acquired other than by contribution shall be determined under part II of subchapter O (sec. 1011 and following).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id440285f3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736">Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68A/249">68A Stat. 249</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
